{"id": "1190828269268901930", "channel_id": "1190828269268901930", "type": 0, "author_id": "780830027822268436", "author_name": "amouroracle", "author_bot": false, "content": "回合五的時候進入額外回合（如背景所示），但是莫名其妙失敗敵人直接攻擊，然後我少了超維空間少了一張牌，進入第六回合，結果打的第一張進去超維空間，右下沒有結束回合或是額外回合的圖標可以按。", "timestamp": "2023-12-31T01:26:23.913000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1190828269755453460", "filename": "IMG_8016.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1674540, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1190828269268901930/1190828269755453460/IMG_8016.png?ex=69cc7440&is=69cb22c0&hm=97f8a2b68bb799d639c5bd8d4073c2be3f592ffd9b6931666196e60aceb510f8&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1190828269268901930", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」超維隊進入額外回合失敗", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
