{"id": "1190923964491505765", "channel_id": "1190720692925243512", "type": 0, "author_id": "1190712196783677542", "author_name": "energetic_cheetah_58696", "author_bot": false, "content": "我只能說 玩過殺戮尖塔的我 可以確定是有問題的 差別就只是官方要認定是bug還是正常設定 因為如果能無限的話一回合要打出多少傷害都能辦到", "timestamp": "2023-12-31T07:46:39.432000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1190720692925243512", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」不能無限抽牌是遊戲機制還是bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1190929255853469786", "channel_id": "1190720692925243512", "type": 0, "author_id": "1183805648929042473", "author_name": "shuaidaobaole", "author_bot": false, "content": "抽牌堆每回合只能刷新一次，不像杀戮尖塔那样是无限刷新的，这是为了防止卡组运转类的效果不可控而设置的上限。", "timestamp": "2023-12-31T08:07:40.991000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1190720692925243512", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」不能無限抽牌是遊戲機制還是bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1190936054723784704", "channel_id": "1190720692925243512", "type": 0, "author_id": "1190712196783677542", "author_name": "energetic_cheetah_58696", "author_bot": false, "content": "遊戲裡有提到這個限制嗎 我是沒看到這個說明🥲🥲", "timestamp": "2023-12-31T08:34:41.968000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1190720692925243512", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」不能無限抽牌是遊戲機制還是bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
